vernac_cmds: Definition eqf(m:fmap)(x y:dart):= expf m x y \/ expf m y x.
Lemma refl_eqf : forall (m:fmap)(x:dart), exd m x -> eqf m x x.
Lemma symm_eqf : forall (m:fmap)(x y:dart), eqf m x y -> eqf m y x.
Lemma trans_eqf : forall (m:fmap), inv_qhmap m -> forall (x y z:dart), eqf m x y -> eqf m y z -> eqf m x z.
Lemma eqf_dec : forall (m:fmap)(x y:dart), {eqf m x y} + {~eqf m x y}.

Fixpoint eqc(m:fmap)(x y:dart){struct m}:Prop:= match m with V => False | I m0 x0 => x=x0 /\ y=x0 \/ eqc m0 x y | L m0 _ x0 y0 => eqc m0 x y \/ eqc m0 x x0 /\ eqc m0 y0 y \/ eqc m0 x y0 /\ eqc m0 x0 y end.
Lemma eqc_dec : forall (m:fmap)(x y:dart), {eqc m x y} + {~eqc m x y}.
Lemma refl_eqc: forall(m:fmap)(x:dart), exd m x -> eqc m x x.
Lemma symm_eqc: forall(m:fmap)(x y:dart), eqc m x y -> eqc m y x.
Lemma trans_eqc: forall(m:fmap)(x y z:dart), eqc m x y -> eqc m y z -> eqc m x z.
Lemma succ_eqc_A_r : forall m:fmap, inv_qhmap m -> forall (k:dim)(x:dart), succ m k x -> eqc m x (A m k x).
Lemma pred_eqc_A_1_r : forall m:fmap, inv_qhmap m -> forall (k:dim)(x:dart), pred m k x -> eqc m x (A_1 m k x).
Lemma eqc_eqc_A_1_l : forall m:fmap, inv_qhmap m -> forall (k:dim)(x y:dart), eqc m x y -> pred m k x -> eqc m (A_1 m k x) y.
Lemma eqc_A_1_l_eqc : forall m:fmap, inv_qhmap m -> forall (k:dim)(x y:dart), pred m k x -> eqc m (A_1 m k x) y -> eqc m x y.

Lemma expf_A_1_l_eqc : forall m:fmap, inv_qhmap m -> forall (x y:dart)(k:dim), expf m (A_1 m k x) y -> eqc m x y.

Lemma expf_A_r_eqc : forall(m:fmap)(k:dim), inv_qhmap m -> forall (x y:dart), expf m x (A m k y) -> eqc m x y.
generalize (expf_exd_exd m x (A m k y)).
Fixpoint nd(m:fmap):Z := match m with V => 0 | I m0 x => nd m0 + 1 | L m0 _ _ _ => nd m0 end.
Fixpoint nv(m:fmap):Z := match m with V => 0 | I m0 x => nv m0 + 1 | L m0 di0 x y => nv m0 | L m0 di1 x y => nv m0 - if eq_dart_dec (A (clos m0) di1 x) y then 0 else 1 end.
Fixpoint ne(m:fmap):Z := match m with V => 0 | I m0 x => ne m0 + 1 | L m0 di0 x y => ne m0 - if eq_dart_dec (A (clos m0) di0 x) y then 0 else 1 | L m0 di1 x y => ne m0 end.

Fixpoint nf(m:fmap):Z := match m with V => 0 | I m0 x => nf m0 + 1 | L m0 di0 x y => let mc := clos m0 in let x0 := A mc di0 x in let x_1:= A_1 mc di1 x in nf m0 + if eq_dart_dec y x0 then 0 else if expf_dec mc x_1 y then 1 else -1 | L m0 di1 x y => let mc := clos m0 in let x1 := A mc di1 x in let y0 := A mc di0 y in nf m0 + if eq_dart_dec y x1 then 0 else if expf_dec mc x y0 then 1 else -1 end.
Fixpoint nc(m:fmap):Z := match m with V => 0 | I m0 x => nc m0 + 1 | L m0 _ x y => nc m0 - if eqc_dec (clos m0) x y then 0 else 1 end.
Definition ec(m:fmap): Z:= nv m + ne m + nf m - nd m.
Theorem even_ec : forall m:fmap, Zeven (ec m).
